{"tid":1553964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(重要) 有關平野鈴子可能係日本極右，我建議唔好過份神化佢地","createTime":"2019-09-08T19:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T01:29:55.000Z","uid":222970,"like":7,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"88d513c97d7a92618d848ce302541fdb01d4d1f4","tid":1553964,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:30:24.000Z","msg":"認真 如果連登仔過份實化日本極右係冇好處<br />\n<br />\n因為日本極右佢地唔係民主國家既普世價值<br />\n佢地係唔承認南京大屠殺 支持軍國主義<br />\n<br />\n首先國際會唔認同 鬼佬對仇恨主義好反感<br />\n<br />\n而且會令到少部份清醒大陸人反感 eg 陳秋實<br />\n<br />\n萬一國際讉責我地香港人同日本極右合作就大獲<br />\n<br />\n同日本極右合作 對香港運動係冇幫助 好不利<br />\n<br />\n所以上次民間記者會有日本國旗 我不太認同<br />\n<br />\n倒不如搵 人權組織d嘉賓仲好 國際間較容易接受<br />\n<br />\n所以我地同美國國會 人權組織合作絕對冇問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以請三思！"},{"pid":"369ecf84957fda22071ab80d6a47d74a65e1117d","tid":1553964,"uid":271617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:30:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9qD0StPLq6M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9qD0StPLq6M&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=858a93bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9qD0StPLq6M</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際文宣] 我要聽朝成個 FB TWITTER 都見到呢條片！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1552463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1552463</a>"},{"pid":"d7bae51d0b859a971db9fe648406d1ff6a5726bd","tid":1553964,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53908f5b3784a79982f5a98192375422271637a5","tid":1553964,"uid":41662,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:34:26.000Z","msg":"周婷吸左 呢件吸右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /